{"type": "article", "id": 13106, "title": "像“大白”的音箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-06T06:49:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145944yh4cN1zIiHj2FTle.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t现在得了一种“看见长条状有两个眼睛的物体就觉得像大白”的病，你看这个音箱，是不是就很像？这是 Symbol Audio 推出的一款桌面音箱，它有一个优质的低音喇叭，并且 2.1 通道扬声器支持各种输入方式。同时，音箱配备蓝牙接收模块，可以与任何支持蓝牙的设备配合，进行播放。产品有四种配色：胡桃木，橡木，灰色，黑白色，可配合不同装修风格挑选适合的颜色。最后送上<a href=\"http://www.symbolaudio.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Symbol Audio 的官方主页</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407321toC3eOQ2E6HyaBM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261407321tShs79acowFKXmj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140733a6TNfQcDBuiyAnmx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140733OVgicXJLGCKedZ7M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140734x0D9uNFCHt4gf1mG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}